How one does not grow  does not increase in profitable ideas this disappointment the Blessed One teaches with the words But then What is open it soddens not   so one should open out so as to be safe from that disappointment  It is in virtue of three ideas that there is no rainsoddening   in virtue of perception of ugliness one is not rainsoddened  by lust
in virtue of lovingkindness one is not rainsoddened  by hate
