There is the dark kind and yet its existence is in a state with future reappearance  as the bright type of person owing to profitable action to be felt in some future period 
and there is the bright kind and yet its existence is in a state with future rearising as the dark type of person owing to unprofitable action to be felt in some future period   Reversal In the case of the  dark  types the opposite is the  bright types 
