The words  
deal with corruption The words It is by depending on the essentials of existence that this suffering has actual being  down to   His craving for being comes to be abandoned And he no more expectantly relishes nonbeing  deal with penetration The words That bhikkhu being quenched through not assuming no more his being comes to be renewed
