Herein what is the Mode of Conveying a Teaching
In this Thread the three Searches are taught the path of quiet in sensualdesire search is through  ideas that have entered the ear  the path of quiet in the existence search is  through the verbally consolidated 
the path of quiet in the divinelife search is through the well penetrated by right view
Investigation According as he is giving attention to is investigating what is heard he obtains understanding consisting in what is heard
According as he gives attention to  the ideas as heard then he obtains understanding consisting in cogitation
According as he gives attention to ideas here and now then he obtains understanding consisting in keeping in being
This is the Investigation
It is through what is heard that he obtains understanding consisting in what is heard
it is through cogitation that he obtains understanding consisting in cogitation it is through right view that he obtains understanding consisting in keeping in being
There is this Construing
