 Herein the painful way with sluggish acquaintanceship kept in being and made much of fulfills the first meditation The first meditation fulfilled fulfils the first foundation of mindfulness The first foundation of mindfulness fulfilled fulfils the first abiding The first abiding fulfilled fulfils the first right endeavour The first right endeavour fulfilled fulfils the first wonderful and marvellous idea The first wonderful and marvellous idea fulfilled fulfills the first expression The first expression fulfilled fulfils concentration due to will Concentration due to will fulfilled fulfils faculty restraint Faculty restraint fulfilled fulfills lovingkindness
